title: Milk Crown H!
original_name: ミルククラウン H!(ハイ!)
sinopse: Continuing one year after "Milk Crown," Oto and Jin have to hide their love, since a relation between maid and pupil is not allowed. But Oto's "brother" (not related by blood) Ise and Jin's old acquaintance Ura are sure to spell trouble for them...
